Removed 35 lines of duplicated code from `agr/commands/sync.py`. The grouped remote install loop had a single-entry special case (using `prepare_repo_for_skill`) that duplicated the multi-entry path (using `prepare_repo_for_skills`). Since `prepare_repo_for_skills` handles single skills correctly (it delegates to the same `_checkout_sparse_paths` function), the special case was unnecessary. All 576 tests pass.
